  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK658">
<l>kaṭinta kaṭintorār ceyvārk kavaitā </l>
<l> muṭintālum pīḻai tarum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The actions of those, who have not desisted from doing deeds forbidden (by the great), will, even if they succeed, cause them sorrow.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
